<title type="html"><![CDATA[Condition of Ibn Sireen’s Book About Dreams – Shaykh Muhammad Nasiruddin al-Albani]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="https://forum.salafiri.com/viewtopic.php?t=396&amp;p=425#p425"><![CDATA[
Shaykh al-Albaani was asked the following question:<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Question:</span></strong><br /><br />السؤال :<br />عندي كتاب منسوب لابن سيرين ؟<br /><br />I have a book ascribed to Ibn Sireen (so what do you say regarding it)?<br /><br /><strong><span style="color: #0000FF">Answer:</span></strong><br /><br />الجواب :<br />لابن سيرين في المنامات ؟ حسبك أنه كتاب منامات ، لا يعتمد عليه<br /><br />Ibn Sireen about dreams ? It is sufficient for you to know that the Book on dreams is not relied upon”.<br /><br /><em>[Silsilatul Huda wan-Nur no. 93]</em><br /><br />Translated by<br /><br />Faisal Ibn Abdul Qaadir Ibn Hassan<br />Abu Sulaymaan<br /><br />Source: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://torontodawah.com/index.php/2015/09/01/condition-of-ibn-sireens-book-about-dreams-shaykh-muhammad-nasiruddin-al-albani/">http://torontodawah.com/index.php/2015/ ... al-albani/</a><!-- m --><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="https://forum.salafiri.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=56">Shehzad Sattar</a> — Sat Sep 17, 2016 12:21 am</p><hr />
